{"tid":1988580,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] browser唔識開link淨係識download","createTime":"2020-04-25T09:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T16:31:29.000Z","uid":204746,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f6ada721b72f737e55348921d64bfd39f9e63813","tid":1988580,"uid":204746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T09:59:55.000Z","msg":"我部mac無論safari定chrome都係唔識自己開link<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如我㩒youtube某一條片咁，正路應該自動波開條link架嘛，但而家佢會變左download html file<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我用公司pc登入同一個google account係正常冇咁既問題，所以應該唔關account事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經試過restart mac，reinstall埋chrome都唔得，又試過用防毒掃又掃唔到啲咩<br />\n<br />\n我google左好耐都搵唔到答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人有遇過/知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906b1a9ed9a3833793e2c41d8759a11399c29e76","tid":1988580,"uid":247203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T20:31:43.000Z","msg":"Safe mode 試過？"},{"pid":"1cb42ad9533fac5bb6a83980c9d6685de5989746","tid":1988580,"uid":199718,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T20:33:29.000Z","msg":"壓住左個ctrl制"},{"pid":"95219647d8608947faeb75f1acd287debc15b79e","tid":1988580,"uid":34684,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1cb42ad9533fac5bb6a83980c9d6685de5989746","tid":1988580,"uid":199718,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T20:33:29.000Z","msg":"壓住左個ctrl制"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T20:40:44.000Z","msg":"應該係alt"},{"pid":"9e5763fe0bc0f267da706cdc7de669090a264299